Maintainer: Carlos Holbig <carlos.holbig@gmail.com>
Description: This package access Eta Model Climate Change data of South America 
    generated from Eta Model of CPTEC/INPE (Brazil) for a historical period 
    between 1960 to 2005 and a prevision period between 2006 to 2100. This data 
    are available from the PROJETA repository (https://projeta.cptec.inpe.br/). 
    The EtaModelCC is an R package developed by Mosaico research group at 
    University of Passo Fundo (Brazil).
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
